The edges of layer $L$ are defined by the 6 directions. Let $n$ be a number in layer $L$. Its neighbors are:
- One neighbor at $n - \delta_1$ (in $L-1$)
- One neighbor at $n - \delta_2$ (in $L-1$)
- Four neighbors in $L$ (two following, two preceding).

